<h3 id="인덱싱indexing">인덱싱(Indexing)</h3>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># 기본 파이썬 문법처럼 indexing 가능
</span><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span> 
