<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>array([ 1,  8, 15, 22])
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># 전체 행에 대해서, 1, 2번 컬럼 참조
