<h2 id="배열-값-삽입수정삭제복사">배열 값 삽입/수정/삭제/복사</h2>

<h3 id="배열-값-삽입">배열 값 삽입</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">insert()</code>: np.insert(arr, obj, values, axis=None)</li>
  <li>배열의 특정 위치에 값 삽입</li>
  <li>axis를 지정하지 않으면 1차원 배열로 변환</li>
  <li>추가할 방향을 axis로 지정</li>
  <li>원본 배열 변경없이 새로운 배열 반환</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">b1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">insert</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">b1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[1 2 3]
[10  1  2  3]
[1 2 3]
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">insert</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;function numpy.insert(arr, obj, values, axis=None)&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="배열-값-수정">배열 값 수정</h3>

<ul>
  <li>배열의 인덱싱으로 접근하여 값 수정</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">a</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">8</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[1 2 3]
[8 2 3]
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="배열-값-삭제">배열 값 삭제</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">delete()</code>: np.delete(arr, obj, axis=None)</li>
  <li>배열의 특정 위치에 값 삭제</li>
  <li>axis를 지정하지 않으면 1차원 배열로 변환</li>
  <li>삭제할 방향을 axis로 지정</li>
  <li>원본 배열 변경없이 새로운 배열 반환</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">delete</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[8 2 3]
[2 3]
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="배열-복사">배열 복사</h3>

<ul>
  <li>리스트 자료형과 달리 배열의 슬라이스는 복사본이 아님(원본배열에 영향을 줌,동일한 메모리위치에 있는걸 가져옴)</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">a_sub</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a_sub</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">a_sub</span><span class="p">[::]</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a_sub</span><span class="p">)</span>
